<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Chen's blog (Posts about cuisine)</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="http://redguardtoo.github.io/categories/cuisine.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 31 May 2025 02:21:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>蒜苗炒牛肉做法</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/suan-miao-chao-niu-rou-zuo-fa/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.xinshipu.com/%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89%E7%82%92%E8%92%9C%E8%8B%97-83979.htm"&gt;菜谱&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;甜面酱本身带盐了 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;蒜苗可以大火快炒,更嫩一点 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;   &lt;p&gt; &lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/wpid-stir-fried-beef-and-garlic-stem1.jpg" alt="lightbox"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><category>beef</category><category>cuisine</category><category>garlic</category><category>zh</category><guid>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/suan-miao-chao-niu-rou-zuo-fa/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2013 19:53:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>三文鱼炖豆腐做法</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/san-wen-yu-dun-dou-fu-zuo-fa/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4cc524d50102dzgv.html"&gt;菜谱, 全文如下&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;     &lt;pre class="example"&gt;用料:
三文鱼、老豆腐、面粉、黑胡椒粒、甜椒、葱、



大蒜、姜、松子、香菜、盐、老抽、生抽、糖。



做法：

1: 三文鱼去掉鱼骨，拔出鱼刺，和豆腐切成大小相仿的小块，



并用厨房纸巾稍稍擦干水份，三文鱼块里撒入适量的黑胡椒粒，



放入2勺面粉稍微裹以下;



鱼炖豆腐好吃2字诀-三文鱼炖豆腐



2: 其他材料备好;

鱼炖豆腐好吃2字诀-三文鱼炖豆腐



3: 锅底用姜片擦一遍，放入姜片、三文鱼2面煎黄取出，



再放入豆腐块煎黄;

鱼炖豆腐好吃2字诀-三文鱼炖豆腐



4: 倒入适量老抽上色，生抽、盐、糖、大蒜调味，



一次性倒入足量的开水，大火煮开，中火炖至快干;

鱼炖豆腐好吃2字诀-三文鱼炖豆腐



5: 放入甜椒块翻炒一下，撒入松子、香菜段即可起锅。

鱼炖豆腐好吃2字诀-三文鱼炖豆腐





小牛贴心提示：

1：炖豆腐和鱼，想要好吃，关键要时间，

即是老话所说"千滚的豆腐万滚的鱼";



2：鱼块裹面粉、生姜擦锅都能防止鱼不沾锅;



3：一次性加入足量的开水，中途不要频繁加水。

&lt;/pre&gt;  &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;生抽至少两大勺,我放得太少 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;炖得时候我放水太少,一开始就要多放,至少半大碗水 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;鱼和豆腐煎的黄一点,一开始用纸吸干水份较好,否则油到处溅 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;老抽没有了,所以颜色很难看 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;诀窍1,黑胡椒之类的辛香料都是油炸过后才更香 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;诀窍2,如果做汤的话,鱼和豆腐炖的时间越长越好吃,也有营养 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;   &lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="http://www.meishij.net/zuofa/sanwenyudoufutang.html"&gt;另附有三文鱼豆腐汤&lt;/a&gt;的做法 &lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/wpid-salmon-dun-doufu.jpg" alt="http://blog.binchen.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/wpid-salmon-dun-doufu.jpg"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><category>cuisine</category><category>salmon</category><category>soup</category><category>toufu</category><category>zh</category><guid>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/san-wen-yu-dun-dou-fu-zuo-fa/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2013 21:15:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>番茄鸡蛋汤做法</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/fan-qie-ji-dan-tang-zuo-fa/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;放蒜(可以加姜,葱)大火爆炒,也可以加点老抽 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;放入番茄超出茄红素 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;加水煮,调味放盐糖 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;最后放入打碎鸡蛋,五秒钟后起锅 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;有人介绍下面也是类似原理,加葱花老抽爆炒,然后放水煮面 &lt;/p&gt;</description><category>cuisine</category><category>soup</category><category>zh</category><guid>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/fan-qie-ji-dan-tang-zuo-fa/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2013 19:54:19 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>香菇生滚牛肉窝蛋粥做法</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/xiang-gu-shen-gun-niu-rou-wo-dan-zhou-zuo-fa/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.meishij.net/zuofa/xianggushenggunniurouwodanzhou.html"&gt;菜谱&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;香菇先用冷水冲洗,然后25度温水浸泡至少1小时,浸泡后的水也要放到粥里 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;小火1到1.5小时后粥基本烂了,不断搅拌粥 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;牛肉最后开大火加入过一下,可能是为了避免把牛肉烧老 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;蛋是用粥捂熟的,据说很经典的技巧,就是要蛋白和粥混在一起,但是蛋黄半熟还是完整的 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;如果粥觉得不够味可以加盐和鲜露(家乐牌鲜露) &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-beef-porridge.jpg" alt="http://blog.binchen.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-beef-porridge.jpg"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><category>cuisine</category><category>porrige</category><category>zh</category><guid>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/xiang-gu-shen-gun-niu-rou-wo-dan-zhou-zuo-fa/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2013 16:58:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>韩国大酱汤做法</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/han-guo-da-jiang-tang-zuo-fa/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;买酱,见下图 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-korean-soup-sauce.jpg" alt="http://blog.binchen.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-korean-soup-sauce.jpg"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;倒入白菜，菇，韩国豆芽等等，加冷水，煮开 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;倒入酱，加糖盐调味 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-korean-soup.jpg" alt="http://blog.binchen.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-korean-soup.jpg"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><category>cuisine</category><category>korean</category><category>soup</category><category>zh</category><guid>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/han-guo-da-jiang-tang-zuo-fa/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2013 19:45:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>苦瓜胡萝卜炒鸡蛋做法</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/ku-gua-hu-luo-bo-chao-ji-dan-zuo-fa/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.xinshipu.com/%E8%8B%A6%E7%93%9C%E8%83%A1%E8%90%9D%E5%8D%9C%E7%85%8E%E8%9B%8B-83797.htm"&gt;菜谱&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;尽量切小丁 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;*小火*煎蛋 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;我先炒了胡萝卜 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-bitter-melon-carrot-fried-egg.jpg" alt="http://blog.binchen.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-bitter-melon-carrot-fried-egg.jpg"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><category>carrot</category><category>cuisine</category><category>egg</category><category>zh</category><guid>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/ku-gua-hu-luo-bo-chao-ji-dan-zuo-fa/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2013 18:31:21 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Take bavarian tasting platter at Bavarian Bier Cafe Parramatta</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/take-bavarian-tasting-platter-at-bavarian-bier-cafe-parramatta/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://maps.google.com.au/maps?client=ubuntu&amp;amp;channel=fs&amp;amp;oe=utf-8&amp;amp;ie=UTF8&amp;amp;q=Bavarian+Bier+Caf%C3%A9+Parramatta&amp;amp;fb=1&amp;amp;gl=au&amp;amp;hq=Bavarian+Bier+Caf%C3%A9&amp;amp;hnear=0x6b12a318e167af4f:0x5017d681632c600,Parramatta+NSW&amp;amp;cid=6547079215207738546&amp;amp;t=m&amp;amp;z=16&amp;amp;vpsrc=0&amp;amp;iwloc=A"&gt;Location at google map&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;"platter" means different kinds of foods in one big platter &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;sausage is good &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;$31 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-bavarian-tasting-platter-01.jpg" alt="http://blog.binchen.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-bavarian-tasting-platter-01.jpg"&gt; &lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-bavarian-tasting-platter-02.jpg" alt="http://blog.binchen.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-bavarian-tasting-platter-02.jpg"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><category>cuisine</category><category>en</category><category>restaurant</category><guid>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/take-bavarian-tasting-platter-at-bavarian-bier-cafe-parramatta/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2013 09:29:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>豆瓣酱盖交饭做法</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/dou-ban-jiang-gai-jiao-fan-zuo-fa/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;这是&lt;a href="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/jw!cGRdXLOAGRRYGVWg9Ac0AKngjaHkfTc-/article?mid=11068"&gt;菜谱&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;一开始油可能要多点，我的猪肉太精了，没有逼出油来 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;豆瓣酱慢慢炒 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-doubanjiang-rice.jpg" alt="http://blog.binchen.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-doubanjiang-rice.jpg"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><category>cuisine</category><category>rice</category><category>zh</category><guid>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/dou-ban-jiang-gai-jiao-fan-zuo-fa/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2013 09:19:11 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>my salad</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/my-salad/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;p&gt;As my friend said,this avocado sauce is better: &lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-avocado-salad.jpg" alt="http://blog.binchen.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-avocado-salad.jpg"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><category>cuisine</category><category>en</category><category>salad</category><guid>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/my-salad/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2013 09:09:17 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>南瓜粥作法</title><link>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/nan-gua-zhou-zuo-fa/</link><dc:creator>Chen Bin</dc:creator><description>&lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;三杯米,南瓜一个 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;南瓜切小块,越小越好,因为不打算煮太长时间粥,而南瓜要完全溶解 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;南瓜切皮的诀窍在于南瓜开水泡两分钟.参考&lt;a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YShXlrDtZXo"&gt;阿基师教你切南瓜皮&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;米要冷水浸泡20分钟 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;放入南瓜和米后,煮开,然后到入麻油(防止粘锅底),小火烧一小时,不断搅拌粥 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;取决于口味可以加糖 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="http://redguardtoo.github.io/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-pumpkin-porridge.jpg" alt="http://blog.binchen.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wpid-pumpkin-porridge.jpg"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><category>cuisine</category><category>porridge</category><category>zh</category><guid>http://redguardtoo.github.io/posts/nan-gua-zhou-zuo-fa/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2013 08:52:00 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>